212
00:17:23,190 --> 00:17:26,530
Aku telah memutuskan untuk mewujudkan mimpi Taiya.

213
00:17:27,220 --> 00:17:29,740
Mimpi Taiya maksudnya…

214
00:17:29,740 --> 00:17:31,490
Membantu anak-anak di seluruh dunia?

215
00:17:31,490 --> 00:17:32,610
Ya.

216
00:17:33,670 --> 00:17:36,960
Dia harus cepat mewujudkan mimpi Boondorio.

217
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:42,020
Jadi sementara dia di luar angkasa, aku akan menjaga anak-anak.

218
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,720
Aku mengerti.

219
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:48,540
Kau benar-benar baik hati, Sakito.

220
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:52,130
